`,(0,I.jsx)(t.p,{children:"The generation procedure begins. You’ll be asked where you want your SSH keys saved. To accept the default location, press the Enter key. The folder’s permissions will restrict it to your use only."}),`
`,(0,I.jsx)(t.p,{children:"You will now be asked to provide a passcode. I strongly recommend that you enter a passcode here. And keep in mind what it is! You can enter no passcode by pressing Enter, but this is not a good idea. A pass composed of three or four unrelated words strung together will produce a very strong pass."}),`
